textAfterTable: I believe I will learn a lot at this University.  Class sizes are smaller which means I can get more individualized assistance if needed.  Also students are encouraged to schedule in Library time so they can study more effectively.  Faculty was very helpful Login to rate or flag the reviews derek from Ft Lauderdale, FL 01/07/2010 Reviewer is A current student here. 10 out of 10 people found this review useful. 2 of 56 Categories Comments Great for these types of students Athletes, honor program students and student that enjoy a small and productive school. Tips for prospective students For those students that coming into this institution my only tip for you is to stay focused on your education and remember that in every class you must study everyday accurately.
